originalText.text: Aweful ! Super will go months without doing  requested repairs. Suddenly turn off water with no explanation. Rat infested, took months to address. No heat in the winter. Property manager fails to answer emails except when they want something like to raise your rent to close to 5k for no services. Fungal infested. How much worse can it get ? Believe me this is a no “Winn” situation !

originalText.text: We have lived in this building for 10 yrs. since Winn took over in 2019, the property has been neglected and management is unresponsive to requests. The lawns and flower beds have been completely ignored so far this spring and the property looks like a dump. It is embarrassing Sometimes they respond in a timely manner but the super is overwhelmed with work and simply can’t keep up. I have submitted service requests only to find out they have been cancelled for unknown reasons. In winter the heat is TERRIBLE. With our new lease this year, not only did they raise the rent, they added PET RENT of $50/month/pet. In a pandemic. When people are already suffering loss of income.
